The network is assigned a specific address or attribute that are usually allotted by the manufacturers and this called Media Access Control or MAC address.   Significance of MAC Address Changer Tools  While we already know that the MAC address changer tools help you to change the unique addresses of your network adapters  it primarily helps protect your network from needless connections.
